      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for CFD simulation must be validated and version-controlled per institutional SQA procedures.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 was used under a documented SQA plan including version control, regression testing, and installation qualification. Required gradation 2 is met."
    },
    {
