      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must reflect the intended operating envelope of the CPB device under clinical research use.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow rates (2–6 L/min) and rotational speeds (1000–3500 RPM). Gradation 2 achieved."
