      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal solver error quantification beyond code verification is not required.",
      "rationale": "Solver error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Iterative convergence was monitored and residuals reduced below 1e-5 for all simulations."
