      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, qualitative justification of model form selection is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) is the accepted standard for CFD hemolysis prediction in rotary blood pumps. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2."
