      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, characterization of test fluid properties is sufficient without full statistical sample characterization.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments used bovine blood with documented hematocrit and plasma-free hemoglobin baseline. Statistical sample characterization beyond this is not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
