      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters must be demonstrably equivalent to experimental conditions used in validation.",
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions applied in CFD simulations were matched to measured experimental inlet/outlet conditions within 2% for flow rate and 1 RPM for rotational speed. Gradation 2 requirement met."
