    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the overall evidence package supports the regulatory decision.",
